      <title>加密货币贷款机构从上一次投机泡沫的废墟中崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/crypto-lenders-emerge-from-the-ashes-of-last-speculative-bubble</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投机泡沫推动比特币首次突破 10 万美元，如今正蔓延至长期受创的加密借贷行业，而这一次，去中心化金融应用占据了主导地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/crypto-lenders-emerge-from-the-ashes-of-last-speculative-bubble</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 17:02:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦警告金融系统仍面临商业房地产和加密货币风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/yellen-warns-financial-system-still-faces-office-space-crypto-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦周五表示，尽管通胀降温和低失业率提振了整体经济，但美国金融体系在 2024 年仍将继续面临商业房地产风险和数字资产带来的脆弱性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/yellen-warns-financial-system-still-faces-office-space-crypto-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 16:48:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加元和加拿大元收益率下跌，因交易员押注加拿大央行大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/loonie-canadian-yields-slump-as-traders-bet-on-big-boc-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于失业率飙升，交易员加大对加拿大央行下周降息半个百分点的押注，加元跌至近五年来最低收盘水平，债券收益率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/loonie-canadian-yields-slump-as-traders-bet-on-big-boc-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 15:40:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街债券卖家期待更大的奖金奖励</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-s-bond-sellers-look-toward-bigger-2024-bonus-rewards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[招聘和薪酬专家表示，帮助公司出售债务的华尔街银行家将在 2024 年获得更大的奖金，如果发行趋势继续下去，明年可能会获得更高的奖励。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-s-bond-sellers-look-toward-bigger-2024-bonus-rewards</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯法令缓解付款担忧，欧洲天然气公司亏损扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/european-gas-extends-losses-with-russian-decree-easing-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫改变了支付俄罗斯天然气的程序，缓解了人们对该地区天然气供应将被切断的担忧，导致欧洲天然气价格本周延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/european-gas-extends-losses-with-russian-decree-easing-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:59:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
